001package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.enums;
002
003import lombok.Getter;
004
005/**
006 * Enum representing various UI features available in the framework.
007 *
008 * <p>Each feature corresponds to a specific UI component or functionality within the test automation framework.
009 * These features help in organizing and accessing different UI-related services dynamically.
010 *
011 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate üíçüë®üíª
012 */
013@Getter
014public enum Features {
015
016   /**
017    * Represents input field interactions in the UI.
018    */
019   INPUT_FIELDS("inputField"),
020
021   /**
022    * Represents table interactions in the UI.
023    */
024   TABLE("table"),
025
026   /**
027    * Represents button field interactions in the UI.
028    */
029   BUTTON_FIELDS("buttonField"),
030
031   /**
032    * Represents radio button field interactions in the UI.
033    */
034   RADIO_FIELDS("radioField"),
035
036   /**
037    * Represents checkbox field interactions in the UI.
038    */
039   CHECKBOX_FIELDS("checkboxField"),
040
041   /**
042    * Represents toggle switch field interactions in the UI.
043    */
044   TOGGLE_FIELDS("toggleField"),
045
046   /**
047    * Represents select dropdown interactions in the UI.
048    */
049   SELECT_FIELDS("selectField"),
050
051   /**
052    * Represents list field interactions in the UI.
053    */
054   LIST_FIELDS("listField"),
055
056   /**
057    * Represents loader field interactions in the UI.
058    */
059   LOADER_FIELDS("loaderField"),
060
061   /**
062    * Represents hyperlink interactions in the UI.
063    */
064   LINK_FIELDS("linkField"),
065
066   /**
067    * Represents alert pop-up interactions in the UI.
068    */
069   ALERT_FIELDS("alertField"),
070
071   /**
072    * Represents tab navigation interactions in the UI.
073    */
074   TAB_FIELDS("tabField"),
075
076   /**
077    * Represents request interception functionality.
078    */
079   REQUESTS_INTERCEPTOR("interceptor"),
080
081   /**
082    * Represents validation mechanisms within the framework.
083    */
084   VALIDATION("validation"),
085
086   /**
087    * Represents navigation actions in the UI.
088    */
089   NAVIGATION("navigation"),
090
091   /**
092    * Represents data insertion functionality for UI components.
093    */
094   DATA_INSERTION("insertionService");
095
096   /**
097    * The associated field name for the feature.
098    */
099   private final String fieldName;
100
101   /**
102    * Constructs a UI feature with the specified field name.
103    *
104    * @param fieldName The corresponding field name for the feature.
105    */
106   Features(final String fieldName) {
107      this.fieldName = fieldName;
108   }
109}
